Try to use `pathRewrite` callback to retrieve information about url path.

Example:

```
&quot;**/v1/myApi&quot;: {
  &quot;pathRewrite&quot;: (path) =&gt; {
      if (path.includes(&#39;param=bar&#39;)) {
          return &quot;/mocks/response1.mock.json&quot;;
      }
      return &quot;/mocks/response2.mock.json&quot;;
  }
}
```

